013\/02\/07\/yawm-al-qiyamah-barefoot\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Resurrection: People resurrected barefoot, naked, uncircumcised","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will be assembled barefoot, naked, and uncircumcised.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, will the men and women look at each other?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe matter will be too serious for them to notice.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31914,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/hijab-women-blind-men\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Women veiling themselves from men, even blind men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: While we were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Ibn Maktum was given permission to enter. He entered and that was after the command to veil. The Prophet said, \u201cVeil yourselves from him.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is he not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/16\/modesty-men-women-naked\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Guarding chastity by modesty with nakedness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man should not look at the nakedness of another man, and a woman should not look at the nakedness of another woman. A man should not lie with another man under a single blanket,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11676,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/23\/haya-modesty-mind-body-soul\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Be modest with Allah in mind, body, soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe modest before Allah, as is His right.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, surely we have modesty, all praise is due to Allah!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is not so. Rather, modesty before Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/entire-deen-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Haya: All of Islam revolves around modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurrah ibn Iyas reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when modesty was mentioned to him. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is modesty part of the religion?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cRather, it is the entire religion.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, modesty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/17\/prohibition-describing-sex\/","url_meta":{"origin":18825,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Prohibition of verbally describing sexual features","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA woman should not touch another woman and then describe her figure to her husband as if he were gazing at her.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5240 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18825","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/pos